PrecisAuthority for THE ST. LAWRENCE SEAWAY AUTHORITY to sign a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT with ONTARIO HYDRO that amends the 30-year lease granted to Hydro in 1978 which allows them to draw water and occupy land at THOROLD, ONTARIO, by revising the method of calculating water rental fees for the next twenty years (1988-2008).

precis:
Authority for THE ST. LAWRENCE SEAWAY AUTHORITY to sign a SUPPLEMENTARY
AGREEMENT with ONTARIO HYDRO that amends the 30-year lease granted to Hydro
in 1978 which allows them to draw water and occupy land at THOROLD,
ONTARIO, by revising the method of calculating water rental fees for the
next twenty years (1988-2008).
